                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-169-victim903 t18250113-169-viclabel895"></join>. The witness Elderfield lives opposite to me - on the 8th of December, she gave me information; I went out and saw the prisoner running - my man followed and brought her back - I found a pelisse on her which had hung at the door.</p>
