            . I live opposite to Mr. Burgess. I saw the prisoner take down the pelisse and run away with it. I gave the alarm and she was stopped. It had hung just within side the door.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The Prisoner put in a written defence, pleading distress, and two witnesses gave her a very good character.</p>
